text:
I'm sincerely hoping @Apple  stops doing business with @UPS going forward. Haven't even got any updates from @UPSHelp after having my package delayed for 5 days. 

#badservice #ups #apple #iphone #delivery #Toronto
@marwanalany That sounds frustrating. I'd like to look into this for you. Please DM your tracking number, complete address and best contact number. ^KS https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
@UPSHelp Still nothing. How many days does it usually take to get a response from your customer service?
@marwanalany I am showing that this package is waiting to be released from the third party broker. Once this is released we will get it delivered for you. ^AC
@UPSHelp I'm sorry, but what does that even mean? Why is there a 3rd party broker?
@marwanalany The shipper has hired another company to be the broker for these packages. Once this is resolved they will get this package back to UPS and we will get it delivered. ^AC
